                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320517-247-victim1840 t18320517-247-viclabel1430"></join>. On the 28th of April, about ten o'clock, I was in <placeName id="t18320517-247-crimeloc1431">Fore-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18320517-247-crimeloc1431" type="placeName" value="Fore-street"></interp>
