                     <interp inst="t18320517-247-person1843" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a marshalsman. I heard a witness say the prisoner had gone up Milton-street - I followed, and took him and the boy, but in scuffling with the prisoner the other party let the boy go; I found the handkerchief in the prisoner's pocket.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I beg for mercy.</p>
